{"service_name": "Security Services", "service_id": "7917221930371830", "company_name": "Hunter Macdonald Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Hunter Macdonald Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Security Services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Security Services providing assurance that the cloud solution being delivered achieves the correct level of security, delivered to the highest standards. Hunter Macdonald provides a coherent risk based approach to prioritising and addressing vulnerabilities and defects in the Cloud as part of a CESG Cyber Security Professional Offering.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Security Policy, Security Standards, RMADS, ISO27001, HMG IA Standard 1/2\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Information Security, Security Architecture and Assurance, SPF\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Security Testing, Penetration Testing, CLAS, CCP, HMG security policy compliance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Cloud Specific Digital Forensics, Cyber Incident, Incident Management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Data Integrity, Data Separation, Security Operating Procedures\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     IA Auditor, Risk Advisor and Accreditor Staff\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Protective Marking and Asset Control\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Test Strategy, Test Planning, Test Execution\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Computer Forensics, Mobile Device Forensics\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Network Forensics, Data Analysis Forensics, Database Forensics\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Coherent risk-based approach to prioritising, addressing vulnerabilities and defects\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Adherence to Security Policy Framework and Information Assurance standards\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Verification and validation of security enforcing functions\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Achieving business outcomes using cloud technology as an enabler\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Achieving the required deliverables and outcomes for the client\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Fixed price or SFIA, to best suit your business requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Outcome and deliverable based \u2013 ensuring business benefits are achieved\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Driving delivery and service excellence using the cloud\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Independent and non-prejudiced view, Cyber Essentials Assessment, Cyber Essentials Implementation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     CHECK, CREST, CLAS, CCP qualified, SC Cleared\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3522 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Including VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Education pricing available\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/580285/7917221930371830-pricing-document-2015-10-04-1146.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"ht